          {
            "title": "Lesson #1",
            "id": 132702,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ao escrever SQL no Express, podemos utilizar consultas parametrizadas para tornar o acesso ao banco de dados o mais flexível possível.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 132703,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Consultas parametrizadas são um tipo de consulta SQL em que espaços reservados são usados para valores, que são passados como parâmetros.</p><p>Elas são usadas para tornar o trabalho com dados conveniente, mas também para prevenir ataques de injeção de SQL.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 132718,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Temos uma conexão com um banco de dados que possui uma tabela de usuários com valores dentro.</p><p>Agora podemos criar uma consulta SQL para recuperar uma entrada.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"86\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"95\" endIndex=\"105\" /><option startIndex=\"106\" endIndex=\"126\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>SELECT *</code> seguido de <code>FROM users</code> e finalmente <code>WHERE name = 'Alice'</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132733,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Antes de podermos executá-lo, precisamos prepará-lo com <code>db.prepare</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"87\" /><option startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"88\" /><option startIndex=\"88\" endIndex=\"95\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>db</code> seguido de <code>.</code> e finalmente <code>prepare</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132734,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para manter uma referência da nossa consulta, salvamos em uma variável.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"90\" /><option startIndex=\"91\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option startIndex=\"97\" endIndex=\"98\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>const</code> seguido de <code>query</code> e finalmente <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132732,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Finalmente, podemos executá-lo e registrar o resultado.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = 'Alice'&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" user = query.get();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(user);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"168\" endIndex=\"173\" /><option startIndex=\"173\" endIndex=\"179\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{ id: 378, name: &quot;Alice&quot; }\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>query</code> seguido de <code>.get()</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132735,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>No entanto, uma abordagem muito melhor é usar uma instrução parametrizada com um <code>?</code> que podemos substituir mais tarde pelo valor real.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database = \" /><text value=\"require\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;better-sqlite3&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" db = \" /><text value=\"new\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" Database(\" /><text value=\"&quot;database.db&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" query = db.prepare(\" /><text value=\"&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE name = ?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" user = query.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Alice&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(user);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"131\" endIndex=\"145\" /><option startIndex=\"172\" endIndex=\"179\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"WHERE name = 'Alice'\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"{ id: 378, name: &quot;Alice&quot; }\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>WHERE name = ?</code> seguido de <code>\"Alice\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
